/*
Project structure:

my_project/
├── include/
│   ├── confidential.h          <- Wi-Fi credentials
│   ├── logger.h                <- Interface + serial logger implementation
│   ├── network_manager.h       <- Wi-Fi manager class (was previously called NetworkManager)
├── src/
│   ├── main.cpp                <- Entry point
│   ├── logger.cpp              <- Logger methods
│   ├── network_manager.cpp     <- Wi-Fi methods
└── platformio.ini             <- PlatformIO config
*/